    "description": "This makes the hop circle callback a bit easier to interpret visually. The circles and (still optional) labels are colored from grey to white depending on the particular halo's order in the list of halos (white for the largest), and the text is offset based on the radius of the circle which also aids in readability.\r\n\r\nHere are two cropped and zoomed grabs of the same projection + hop circles (different levels of zoom, sorry). With the [old way, http://screencast.com/t/RWlYLGPDm](http://screencast.com/t/RWlYLGPDm) these halos are impossible to interpret, but with the\r\n[new way, http://screencast.com/t/JckuLCbw](http://screencast.com/t/JckuLCbw), it's clearer.\r\n",
